---
/**
 * ai-infrastructure/0001 · Figure 1 — the HERO "One request, every hop".
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from
 * docs/ai-infrastructure/lessons/0001-the-ai-infra-stack-end-to-end.html
 * (figure + svg + figcaption incl. the footnote <sup>). It lives as an .astro
 * component, NOT inline in the MDX, because MDX's JSX parser is unreliable with
 * raw inline SVG that uses kebab-case attributes (text-anchor, font-size,
 * stroke-width, marker-end, …) and self-referential ids.
 *
 * This is the FIRST figure rendered on the page, so it also carries the source
 * page's shared <defs> arrowhead markers (#arw / #arwG / #arwR / #arwM) — in the
 * source these live in one hidden <svg> in <body>; the later figures reference
 * those same page-level ids via marker-end="url(#arw)". Emitting them once here
 * keeps a single definition (no duplicate-id collisions across components).
 */
---

<svg width="0" height="0" style="position:absolute" aria-hidden="true"
    ><defs>
        <marker
            id="arw"
            viewBox="0 0 10 10"
            refX="8.5"
            refY="5"
            markerWidth="7"
            markerHeight="7"
            orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#6b675f"></path></marker
        >
        <marker
            id="arwG"
            viewBox="0 0 10 10"
            refX="8.5"
            refY="5"
            markerWidth="7"
            markerHeight="7"
            orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#2f5d3a"></path></marker
        >
        <marker
            id="arwR"
            viewBox="0 0 10 10"
            refX="8.5"
            refY="5"
            markerWidth="7"
            markerHeight="7"
            orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#9a2417"></path></marker
        >
        <marker
            id="arwM"
            viewBox="0 0 10 10"
            refX="8.5"
            refY="5"
            markerWidth="7"
            markerHeight="7"
            orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#b5179e"></path></marker
        >
    </defs></svg
>

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 640 330"
        role="img"
        aria-label="The end-to-end AI infrastructure request path: text to embedding to vector DB to reranker to model gateway to inference server to response, annotated with where latency, cost, and failure concentrate."
    >
        <text x="320" y="20" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#111110"
            >One request, every hop</text
        >

        <!-- the spine: 7 boxes in two rows -->
        <rect
            x="20"
            y="48"
            width="86"
            height="46"
            rx="8"
            fill="#eef2f7"
            stroke="#1f3a5a"
            stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
        <text x="63" y="68" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-weight="700" fill="#1f3a5a"
            >Query text</text
        >
        <text x="63" y="82" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="#6b675f">user input</text>

        <rect
            x="138"
            y="48"
            width="86"
            height="46"
            rx="8"
            fill="#f6eef7"
            stroke="#b5179e"
            stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
        <text x="181" y="68" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-weight="700" fill="#b5179e"
            >Embedding</text
        >
        <text x="181" y="82" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="#6b675f"
            >text &rarr; vector</text
        >

        <rect
            x="256"
            y="48"
            width="86"
            height="46"
            rx="8"
            fill="#e9f3ec"
            stroke="#2f5d3a"
            stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
        <text x="299" y="65" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-weight="700" fill="#2f5d3a"
            >Vector DB</text
        >
        <text x="299" y="78" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="#6b675f">ANN search</text>
        <text x="299" y="89" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7" fill="#6b675f">HNSW / IVF</text>

        <rect
            x="374"
            y="48"
            width="86"
            height="46"
            rx="8"
            fill="#fbf3e6"
            stroke="#8a5a0f"
            stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
        <text x="417" y="65" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-weight="700" fill="#8a5a0f"
            >Reranker</text
        >
        <text x="417" y="78" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="#6b675f">cross-encoder</text
        >
        <text x="417" y="89" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7" fill="#6b675f">re-score top-K</text>

        <rect
            x="492"
            y="48"
            width="86"
            height="46"
            rx="8"
            fill="#eef2f7"
            stroke="#1f3a5a"
            stroke-width="2"></rect>
        <text x="535" y="65" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-weight="700" fill="#1f3a5a"
            >Gateway</text
        >
        <text x="535" y="78" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="#6b675f">auth · route</text>
        <text x="535" y="89" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7" fill="#6b675f">cache · limit</text>

        <!-- arrows row 1 -->
        <line x1="106" y1="71" x2="134" y2="71" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
        <line x1="224" y1="71" x2="252" y2="71" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
        <line x1="342" y1="71" x2="370" y2="71" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
        <line x1="460" y1="71" x2="488" y2="71" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>

        <!-- wrap down to row 2 -->
        <path
            d="M578,94 C600,110 600,124 578,140"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#6b675f"
            marker-end="url(#arw)"></path>

        <rect
            x="374"
            y="124"
            width="160"
            height="48"
            rx="8"
            fill="#f1eef2"
            stroke="#b5179e"
            stroke-width="2"></rect>
        <text x="454" y="143" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-weight="700" fill="#b5179e"
            >Inference server</text
        >
        <text x="454" y="156" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="#6b675f"
            >KV cache · continuous batching</text
        >
        <text x="454" y="167" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="#6b675f"
            >GPU forward pass</text
        >

        <rect x="220" y="124" width="120" height="48" rx="8" fill="#eef2f7" stroke="#1f3a5a"></rect>
        <text x="280" y="146" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-weight="700" fill="#1f3a5a"
            >Response cache</text
        >
        <text x="280" y="159" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="#6b675f"
            >hit &rarr; skip inference</text
        >

        <rect x="66" y="124" width="120" height="48" rx="8" fill="#e9f3ec" stroke="#2f5d3a"></rect>
        <text x="126" y="146" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-weight="700" fill="#2f5d3a"
            >Tokens stream</text
        >
        <text x="126" y="159" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.5" fill="#6b675f"
            >answer to user</text
        >

        <line x1="374" y1="148" x2="342" y2="148" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
        <line x1="220" y1="148" x2="188" y2="148" stroke="#2f5d3a" marker-end="url(#arwG)"></line>

        <!-- the three-governor annotation -->
        <rect
            x="20"
            y="200"
            width="600"
            height="106"
            rx="10"
            fill="color-mix(in srgb,#1f3a5a 6%,transparent)"
            stroke="#1f3a5a"
            stroke-width="1.2"></rect>
        <text x="320" y="220" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10.5" font-weight="700" fill="#1f3a5a"
            >Where each pain concentrates</text
        >
        <text x="40" y="242" font-size="9" font-weight="700" fill="#9a2417">LATENCY</text>
        <text x="135" y="242" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
            >inference forward pass &amp; queue-wait dominate; ANN search is fast unless over-tuned</text
        >
        <text x="40" y="266" font-size="9" font-weight="700" fill="#8a5a0f">COST</text>
        <text x="135" y="266" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
            >per-token inference; the gateway is the one place to see and cap total spend</text
        >
        <text x="40" y="290" font-size="9" font-weight="700" fill="#2f5d3a">FAILURE</text>
        <text x="135" y="290" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
            >ANN recall gaps · gateway as blast-radius chokepoint · KV memory capping batch size</text
        >
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        The whole track in one picture. Every later lesson zooms into one of these boxes — this
        lesson is the map: <b>what each hop does</b>, and <b
            >where latency, cost, and failure live</b
        >.<sup><a href="#s1" id="r1b">1</a></sup>
    </figcaption>
</figure>
